    <briefdescription>
<para>Emits HealthChangedEvents when solid collisions involve damage dealers. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Listens for SolidCollisionEvents and checks if the source entity has a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1damage_1_1components_1_1DamageDealerComponent" kindref="compound">DamageDealerComponent</ref>. If the target has a <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1health_1_1components_1_1HealthComponent" kindref="compound">HealthComponent</ref>, emits an <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1damage_1_1commands_1_1ApplyDamageCommand" kindref="compound">ApplyDamageCommand</ref>. Resolves the true attacker (instigator) via <ref refid="classhelios_1_1engine_1_1mechanics_1_1spawn_1_1components_1_1EmittedByComponent" kindref="compound">EmittedByComponent</ref> when applicable (e.g. projectiles). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
